description: This file defines a React component named AnalysisPage that provides an interface for selecting media files, running mock object detection analysis, and visualizing detections with bounding boxes and metrics. It includes logic for handling file uploads, rendering previews, simulating detection results, and overlaying detection boxes on media.

methods.name: AnalysisPage
methods.description: Main React functional component providing analysis UI and logic.

methods.name: BoxOverlay
methods.description: Sub-component responsible for rendering a bounding box overlay around detected objects.
